Summary of All Endpoints & Query Parameters
Recipes Endpoints:
    GET /chop/api/recipes: Query parameters: Filter by category, sub_category, nation, region, sort, limit, page.
    POST /chop/api/recipes: Request body with new recipe data.
    GET /chop/api/recipes/{id}: No query parameters.
    PUT /chop/api/recipes/{id}: Request body with updated recipe data.
    GET /chop/api/recipes/{dish}: Query parameters: Filter by category, sub_category, nation, region.
    GET /chop/api/recipes/{id}/ingredients: No query parameters.
    PUT /chop/api/recipes/{id}/ingredients: Request body with updated ingredients.
    PATCH /chop/api/recipes/{id}/ingredients: Request body with updated ingredients.
    GET /chop/api/recipes/{id}/images: No query parameters.
    POST /chop/api/recipes/{id}/images: Request body with image data.

Ingredients Endpoints:
    GET /chop/api/ingredients/{ingredient_name}: Query parameters: sort.
    GET /chop/api/ingredients/{ingredient_name}/recipes: Query parameters: Filter by category, sub_category, nation, region, sort, limit, page.

Nations Endpoints:
    GET /chop/api/nations: Query parameters: sort. 
    GET /chop/api/nations/{nation}/recipes: Query parameters: Filter by category, sub_category, sort, limit, page.

Regions Endpoints:
    GET /chop/api/regions: sort.
    GET /chop/api/regions/{region}/recipes: Query parameters: Filter by category, sub_category, sort, limit, page.
    GET /chop/api/regions/{region}/nations: Query parameters: sort.

Categories Endpoints
    GET /chop/api/categories: Description: Fetch all available categories (e.g., main, appetizer, snack, etc.). Query parameters: sort.

Subcategories Endpoints
    GET /chop/api/subcategories: Description: Fetch all available sub-categories (e.g., vegan, vegetarian, gluten-free). Query parameters: sort.
